					<msContents>
						<summary>
							<p xml:id="regest1">Erwartet <persName ref="p8049" cert="high">Vadian</persName> zur gemeinsamen Reise an die <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basler</placeName> [Zusammenkunft]; von <placeName ref="l587" cert="high">Zürich</placeName> werden <persName ref="p257" cert="high">Werner Beyel</persName>, <persName ref="p1419" cert="high">Johannes Haab</persName>, <persName ref="p1753" cert="high">Leo Jud</persName> und <persName ref="p495" cert="high">Bullinger</persName>, von <placeName ref="l441" cert="high">Schaffhausen</placeName> <persName ref="p2299" cert="high">Hans von Waldkirch</persName>, [<persName cert="high" ref="p21394">Hans Schmid</persName>], <persName ref="p264" cert="high">Benedikt Burgauer</persName> und <persName ref="p2810" cert="high">Erasmus Ritter</persName> hinreisen. Die <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Berner</placeName> eilen den Genfern zu Hilfe. Bittet um Neuigkeiten aus <placeName ref="l1202" cert="high">Schmalkalden</placeName>.</p>
